{
  "stem": "5810.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we ran out again, and it became easier, and easier, and easier.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I did that on a weekly basis almost.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But what happened is that so much was happening in that cafe and around that area that it-- that it became-- I mean, they guarded it much more.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes two.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes three.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It just didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were totally out-- I mean, they were off duty, and this is what they did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went to the cafe and drank and sang their songs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by that time, I have come-- I had come to hate them anyway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know the difference between a German soldier, an SS, or a Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Their uniform was the uniform, and I had to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I needed to survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I did what I had to do then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when that became almost impossible, then it was-- money actually almost didn't buy food, because it was rationed anyway.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the money was good enough to, let's say, pay the rent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I will tell you how much that means to me-- the word pay the rent-- a little bit later.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It didn't buy food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The rations were rations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it became necessary to do something, at least about eating, which we weren't doing anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And money, as I said, wasn't helping.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So on the way to school again, there were stores, grocery stores.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were attended by, of course, Gentile, Belgian Gentiles, who, I remember one particular one just before all this had happened, was not exactly in love with Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That, that much I do remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I thought, well, if I can do it with German soldiers I can certainly hold up a store.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
